July 28, 2017 10:00 AM ET
IT Services

Company Overview of Ripple Labs Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ripple Labs Inc. provides Ripple protocol, an open-source distributed payment network that enables payments to merchants, consumers, and developers. Its payment protocol transforms payments to work like communications. The company was formerly known as OpenCoin, Inc. and changed its name to Ripple Labs Inc. on September 26, 2013. Ripple Labs Inc. was founded in 2012 and is based in San Francisco, California.


