“Using the Ripple solution, we are working on a new commercial payment service for retail customers that will allow them to send money from China to the U.S. and other countries in real-time.” Andrew Fang, General Manager & Head of Innovation and Research at SHRB








“Using blockchain technology, ATB Financial became the first financial institution in Canada to complete an overseas payment in a matter of seconds. The transaction we performed proves we can significantly reduce the time it takes to move money across borders. This could revolutionize banking for our customers.” Curtis Stange, Chief Strategy & Operations Officer at ATB Financial









